{"tid":1075000,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"一人幾首最鍾意嘅舊歌(80年代或以前)","createTime":"2019-03-23T19:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T11:54:16.000Z","uid":239747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6613fc7dc57ea058797f389dd97f27f4f44368f7","tid":1075000,"uid":239747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T19:02:05.000Z","msg":"人越大就越鍾意聽舊歌，慢慢開始識品味舊歌嘅詞同曲，之後就翻唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好聽嘅歌、好嘅詞真係回味幾多年都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:唔係80後 但好鍾意80年代嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.等-陳百強 (1982)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zNgnFnEiFlo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzNgnFnEiFlo&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=66987362\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zNgnFnEiFlo</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 三人行- 詩詩，劉天蘭，林子祥 (1981)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wJLPsV291d0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwJLPsV291d0&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=79195c50\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wJLPsV291d0</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 胭脂扣- 梅艷芳 (1987)<br />\n套戲都係必睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qXWkl0OuRN4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqXWkl0OuRN4&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ae046ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qXWkl0OuRN4</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 真的愛妳- Beyond (1989)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tjCHafQIhFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtjCHafQIhFk&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=1458644b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tjCHafQIhFk</a><br />\n<br />\n英文就比較鍾意60-70年代嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Yesterday - Beatles (1965)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jo505ZyaCbA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fjo505ZyaCbA&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=df2ab759\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jo505ZyaCbA</a><br />\n<br />\n2. Streets of London - Ralph McTell (1969)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DiWomXklfv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDiWomXklfv8&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=910a4b78\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DiWomXklfv8</a><br />\n<br />\n3. Danny&rsquo;s song - Kenny Loggins (1971) <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4FDcTyyXQb8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4FDcTyyXQb8&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=654592c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4FDcTyyXQb8</a><br />\n<br />\n4. The last resort - The Eagles (1976)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p4zR9r9olOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp4zR9r9olOg&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=d5150993\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p4zR9r9olOg</a>"},{"pid":"143767c8e1a486f15959ff31f942a6a91a5e44cb","tid":1075000,"uid":12597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"最冷一天 漣漪<br />\n自己好鍾意慢歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇推介"},{"pid":"5217e4fe67eb90f558e6a088439b967eef5fdfb0","tid":1075000,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T19:13:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/djV11Xbc914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdjV11Xbc914&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8naXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=879d8eb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/djV11Xbc914</a>"},{"pid":"92ff47f859eb0c398f9d0ffe968be1fc089f9e6b","tid":1075000,"uid":239747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s